y":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"你個腦諗既野既解釋權係個官到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e4dd74c95da7358b64bae6de87dffe16862cb9","tid":2514382,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"考慮各項因素後，嚴官以12個月監禁為量刑起點，因被告認罪而減刑至8個月。嚴官明言，本案涉及重大公眾利益，故即使考慮了被告的背景因素及<span class=\"red\">沒有案底，亦不構成減刑因素</span>。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=a49508d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&h=fd68db83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/</a>"},{"pid":"27e6ba6335f013b639d54410679a13032529a41e","tid":2514382,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a33bbe32f7227bf8c413f01cd8a11cc65ab6074","tid":2514382,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"支那狗西"},{"pid":"b07c19e5448cf95b8ad888031558e813d6ec7db5","tid":2514382,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"嚴西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09ca53ffab1091667ff2bdfdccadabf21e87695","tid":2514382,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45de9